{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/3-Military.gif?t=1737084658\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How deep will you go?\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>COLD ABYSS</strong> is a relaxing and atmospheric exploration game set on the bottom of the ocean. Your objective is simple: repair all broken network cables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Director\u2019s Cut version features new levels, an expanded story, and a completely rebuilt movement system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether it\u2019s peace you\u2019re looking for, or something else-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The dark depths of the ocean are the perfect place to unwind after a long day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/1-Fix-Cable.gif?t=1737084658\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take a dive to the ocean floor, a place where you can truly be alone.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An expanded version of the original <strong>COLD ABYSS</strong>, featuring new levels and story segments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improved visuals and gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather artefacts that flesh out the game's setting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/extras/2---Deep-Water-II.gif?t=1737084658\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737084658","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260040/page.bg.jpg?t=1737084658","capsule_image":"https://shared.aka